6:
Aw, come on, Light! A little bit of
slacking off never hurt anyone!
9:
T-taking breaks is important. I just
don't understand why you have to
take one with me!
13:
I want to cuddle something fluffy,
and you like being cuddled. It's a
win-win situation!
16:
Don't worry, I'm a pro at petting soft,
fuzzy animals!
20: E-excuse me?! I am no animal!
25:
Stella! Back from your trip to
Palpebra?
29: Yes. I have something to report.
32:
The pancake stand's seasonal
menu is available starting today.
37:
Well, what are we standing around
for! Let's go right now!
45:
You know me—I always change my
mind on a whim! Now come on!
50:
Lady Elmara, good luck with your
adventuring today!
53:
Heh... Your support has been heard,
and I offer my thanks!
56:
Elmara! Won't you give us a little fan
service?
59:
Sure, sure! What should I do today...
How about a wink?
63:
I don't think I'll ever get used to
seeing you do that...
67:
Yeah? It's pretty fun interacting with
a good audience though.
70:
And chasing after fun is my thing. It's
why I love cuddling with Light and
being an awesome knight!
74: I am not a pet to be played with!
80:
If it isn't our newest recruit! What're
you doing here?
85:
Goodness, I cannot believe you
abandoned your duties to frolic
around here... Come, it's time to
return to Mirea!
88:
I don't understand... Didn't you leave
home to search for your princess
and the relics?
92:
Well, that was part of it? Mostly I just
wanted to run wild for a bit, so I took
a leave of absence and headed out!
97: So you ended up leaving... for fun...
100:
Your freewheeling behavior is simply
inappropriate! A knight of Mirea
should show more discipline!
101:
At the very least, wake up before
noon and train in the afternoon! And
keep your snacking to a minimum
between lunch and dinner!
105:
Nuh-uh, forget that! I'm done
working under strict, boring rules!
110: I'm starting to get a headache...
115:
That's enough! Quit bothering
Elmara already!
116:
Elmara just wants to be true to
herself! Live as the real her!
119:
He sounds... oddly passionate about
this matter.
123: ...Oh, I think I know what this is about.
126:
Apparently, the fans who prefer my
knightly persona have been fighting
with those that prefer my
loosey-goosey self.
135:
Who knows? It's nice to have
passionate fans though!
139:
I'm not exactly sure this is
something to be happy about...
146:
All right, that's enough! Don't you go
fighting over me—even though it is
kind of funny to watch.
150:
Newbie, let's duke it out! I'll even let
you keep your sword while I go
barehanded.
154:
Manage to land a single nick, and
it's your win! I'll go home without a
fuss.
157:
...Hmph, very well! You better not go
back on your word!
159:
You may be strong, but you waste
all your time on tomfoolery! Prepare
to taste defeat!
169:
And that's that! You don't weigh
much, do you?
172:
*swoon* He was no match for you,
Elmara!
178:
My blade and soul belong to both
my country and my princess!
181:
I know it looks like I'm fooling around,
but I'm pretty serious about my fun.
183:
I go all out for things that I'm
interested in. That's how I got strong
in the first place!
187:
So don't you worry. I'll protect Mirea
and Princess Toria no matter what
happens.
193:
And in order to maintain my position
as Mirea's strongest knight...
197:
I'll need to keep up my regimen of
fun! Raise your hands if you want to
come with me to the pancake stand!
200:
...She's so hot when she gets fired
up...
202: Me, me! I want to go!
204:
I wish to accompany you as well!
Teach me your ways!
207:
This meal is about to be far more
lively than we originally planned.
210: I'm looking forward to the pancakes.
215:
What're you doing over there? Come
on, guys!
